lead_paragraph: Acting head coach Jim Grobe said Monday he has talked to Baylor's assistant coaches, all from former coach Art Briles' staff, about staying focused on football for the final four games of the regular season.

headline.print_headline: No. 25 Baylor Tries to Steady Itself After 2 Losses
